node.text: Memphis You Embraced Me From Day 1. So blessed to be a part of this City #GrindCity & to announce my exclusive partnership with @paniniamerica who would celebrate me like this. Go Check it out! #GRZNXTGEN🏀 #whodoyoucollect @alivepaint
